			<section class="content">
				<div class="block">
					<h2>The problem</h2>
					<p>
						Organizations make strategic choices continuously — but rarely represent them
						explicitly. Decisions are implicit. Assumptions go unstated. The rationale
						behind the work is invisible, even to the people doing it.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="block">
					<h2>The model</h2>
					<p>
						Becoming is a formal model for representing organizational strategy as
						machine-readable records. Decisions, assumptions, activities, actors,
						resources, and results — and the relations between them.
					</p>
					<a href="https://github.com/bkmng/becoming" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
